1. Write a program in which 2 integer variables are initialised, one to 10 and another to 22.
Now use two pointers, to fetch each of these values , calculate the sum and difference and print the same.

2. Write a program to swap two variable values, using a pointer.

3. Write a program to create a fibonacci series for 6 terms. First two numbers are stored in two variables i,j.
Use concept of pointer to calculate the fibonacci series.
